agents.description: Our Mission: As your professional real estate advisers, we focus on client satisfaction. Our business is about service and we are not happy until you are happy. Whether it's finding you a home, finding the best loan, or helping you getting the most out of selling your home, we are here to guide you. If there is anything you need, please let me know. About Our Services: We will listen to your needs and wants to establish our goals and objectives. We work as a team to meet the goals and you will continually be in the loop during the entire process. In this fast paced market, We believe communication is key in meeting our goals and building our relationship. Knowing that you are reading this right now, tells me that you are comfortable with the Internet and email and that means you will be able to take advantage of our 24 hour electronic assistant right here on the web. Please use our Website to provide you powerful features such as the access to the MLS through our MLS Wizard to help you narrow down the ideal home (idx.GibbsAndStory.com). Selling your home takes special care and attention in order to get the highest possible price and you can feel free to send us a message in order to get comparable listings and sales in your neighborhood. We would even be glad to visit your home and give you suggestions in preparing your home for sale (before even putting it on the market). Our links section is designed to point you to important information on home shopping, owning and selling. And if you find what you are looking for, then contact us and we will do our best to get you an answer or point you to a resource. Satisfied clients are the key to our success: Satisfied clients are our best resource for new business. In this very competitive business of real estate, service makes the difference. Our service is second to none and has earned us a valuable source of referrals. If you are considering a real estate professional, please give The Gibbs & Story Team an opportunity to earn your business too. We are confident you will be very happy! Thank you! Troy Gibbs & Johana Story

agents.description:
Keeping up with a changing Real-Estate industry and inspired by the knowledge that there are a growing number of Sellers searching for alternative commission choices, Ken and Janet Carroll opened Integrity Choice Realty, Inc.

Integrity Choice Realty, Inc. was designed to offer sellers choices.  Choices that are more favorable to the seller's "Bottom Line" and a choice in the control of the sale of their home. We understand that our client's home is usually the largest investment they have made for their family and we desire to help them retain more of their equity instead of feeling that they have no options when the time comes to sell.  

As a leading innovative company in the Real-Estate field, we are striving to offer every client superior service as well as a Guaranteed Plan of action in the sale of their home. Please feel free to call us for more information concerning any of our marketing plans. 

Our Company's President/Broker, Ken Carroll, has been in the Real Estate Industry as a leader among Realtors and Sales Managers since 1987. His wife, Janet Carroll, has been dynamic in the field of Real Estate since 1990 and is a vital part of Integrity Choice Realty, Inc. as the Listing Manager. Ken and Janet have been married for 23 years and are parents to four children.  Along with a team of professionals, our ultimate goal is always to "Wow" our clients. 

Since buying or selling a home is in the top three "stressors" in a person's life, our commitment as your local Real Estate Team is to provide you with as stress free of a transaction as possible. We accomplish this task by being a full-time Team of Experts that keeps you apprised of all the information you need in real-time. From searching for your dream home to making an offer and negotiating the terms, or listing your home and accepting a suitable contract, we will be with you all the way. We work on your behalf , always!
